00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:22,080
 the person in front of you that you were having lunch

397
00:23:22,080 --> 00:23:25,040
 or dinner or breakfast with, there's a barrier

398
00:23:25,040 --> 00:23:26,360
 and then there's you. It's transparent,

399
00:23:26,360 --> 00:23:28,080
 but there was still something between you.

400
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:29,520
 Do we remember that?

401
00:23:29,520 --> 00:23:31,600
 Or have we chosen to put that away

402
00:23:31,600 --> 00:23:34,600
 and never think about it again?

403
00:23:34,600 --> 00:23:37,320
 Well, the picture I had was that this room was full

404
00:23:37,320 --> 00:23:39,920
 of people with barriers, these transparent barriers.

405
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:44,920
 And these transparent barriers were between them and God.

406
00:23:44,920 --> 00:23:47,360
 Now they thought they knew God.

407
00:23:47,360 --> 00:23:51,960
 They thought that they had a relationship and they do,

408
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:54,040
 but there is a barrier.

409
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:58,040
 And what God was saying, to remove the barrier

410
00:23:58,040 --> 00:24:01,640
 so that you do not hold back.

411
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:04,240
 There is nothing between you and God.

412
00:24:05,280 --> 00:24:07,080
 Some of us feel that there are things

413
00:24:07,080 --> 00:24:10,600
 that we cannot talk about or say to God.

414
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:12,440
 That's not true.

415
00:24:12,440 --> 00:24:16,000
 And I felt that God really wanted to impress upon us

416
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:19,400
 as we enter into a new year in 2025.

417
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,560
 And if you're part of the Vine,

418
00:24:20,560 --> 00:24:22,600
 as we enter into this new season of,

419
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:26,080
 what does it mean to go and take action for God?

420
00:24:26,080 --> 00:24:30,400
 We have to have the relationship with God

421
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:34,320
 where there are no barriers and that we can go to Him

422
00:24:34,320 --> 00:24:36,640
 with everything that we have.

423
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:41,000
 And so as I thought about some different areas

424
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:44,960
 that I believe in this room, those watching,

425
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:50,000
 are struggling with that are real barriers for you.

