00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:53,360
 And so I wanna mention a few of them

427
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:55,720
 and maybe that's something that resonates with you.

428
00:24:55,720 --> 00:24:58,920
 But I would say, as I was praying earlier,

429
00:24:58,920 --> 00:25:02,280
 thinking about how do I lead this response?

430
00:25:02,280 --> 00:25:03,120
 What does it look like?

431
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:04,480
 I haven't scripted this.

432
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:06,480
 So how do I lead this?

433
00:25:06,480 --> 00:25:09,120
 I felt that God was saying, do you know what?

434
00:25:09,120 --> 00:25:10,640
 Don't hold back as a message

435
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:12,900
 for every single one of you in this room.

436
00:25:12,900 --> 00:25:15,600
 Every single one of you.

437
00:25:15,600 --> 00:25:19,840
 And so we all can respond.

438
00:25:19,840 --> 00:25:22,080
 But I also felt that God wanted to share

439
00:25:22,080 --> 00:25:24,480
 a couple of specific things.

440
00:25:24,480 --> 00:25:26,800
 And the reason why He wants to do that

441
00:25:26,800 --> 00:25:31,800
 is to show you specifically, individually,

442
00:25:32,240 --> 00:25:37,240
 how real God is and how much He knows your situation.

443
00:25:37,240 --> 00:25:41,800
 Because it's pretty general, right?

444
00:25:41,800 --> 00:25:43,000
 Don't hold back.

445
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:49,880
 So as I share these different specific areas,

446
00:25:49,880 --> 00:25:53,560
 then if that relates to you,

447
00:25:53,560 --> 00:25:55,760
 then we're gonna be praying for you.

448
00:25:55,760 --> 00:25:57,260
 We'd love to pray for you.

449
00:25:57,260 --> 00:26:00,120
 And again, I believe that the Holy Spirit

