00:26:00,120 --> 00:26:01,720
 in the picture that I saw,

451
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:04,440
 He was actually just removing all the barriers.

452
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:07,000
 It wasn't difficult to remove those barriers.

453
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:08,960
 You know, you just unplugged it

454
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:10,840
 and it was out the restaurant.

455
00:26:10,840 --> 00:26:12,720
 You know, for God, this is not,

456
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:17,000
 He removes barriers by the power of His Holy Spirit.

457
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:19,640
 And that is what He wants to do.

458
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:24,640
 So we enter 2025 with nothing in the way

459
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:27,360
 of our relationship with God.

