00:26:42,840 --> 00:26:46,200
 You're in a relationship and you have not talked

465
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:48,140
 to God about it at all.

466
00:26:48,140 --> 00:26:51,360
 Because you're afraid of what God will say.

467
00:26:51,360 --> 00:26:53,080
 It's almost like you have this assumption

468
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:54,600
 that He's not gonna be happy about it.

469
00:26:54,600 --> 00:26:57,020
 And so therefore, you're not talking to Him about it,

470
00:26:57,020 --> 00:26:59,400
 where actually, more than anything,

