00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:53,000
 You feel you can't talk about this

486
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:57,000
 because it's something that you've hidden for so long.

487
00:27:57,000 --> 00:28:00,440
 And yet God would say to you, "I see you.

488
00:28:00,440 --> 00:28:04,680
 "Talk to me, don't hold back."

489
00:28:04,680 --> 00:28:09,440
 Often our identities are wrapped in what other people think.

490
00:28:09,440 --> 00:28:11,840
 But actually, God is saying,

491
00:28:11,840 --> 00:28:16,840
 "The number one person that you should think about

492
00:28:16,840 --> 00:28:21,640
 "how they think about you is God," person and divine.

493
00:28:22,080 --> 00:28:22,920
 Divine.

494
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:25,520
 So don't hold back.

