00:28:25,520 --> 00:28:28,440
 I sensed also that in the room,

496
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:33,440
 there was pressure from lots of different,

497
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:38,160
 probably family, I would say, but also maybe friends.

498
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:40,640
 Pressure that is building up pressure within you,

499
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:44,200
 and you're feeling also pressure about being a Christian.

500
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:47,680
 You're feeling the pressure of how you need to perform

501
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:50,940
 for your family, for other people, and for God.

502
00:28:51,740 --> 00:28:52,580
 And God would say to you,

503
00:28:52,580 --> 00:28:57,580
 "I do not expect you to perform in any way.

504
00:28:57,580 --> 00:29:02,820
 "I just want you to have the relationship with me.

505
00:29:02,820 --> 00:29:05,260
 "Come to me, don't hold back."

