00:29:22,100 --> 00:29:27,100
 It's like, God is desperate for you to talk to him

513
00:29:27,100 --> 00:29:31,660
 because we don't.

514
00:29:31,660 --> 00:29:36,540
 We are afraid, we're so afraid.

